Link APP is compatible with all ALCATEL ONETOUCH mobile WiFi supporting 4G LTE High Speed. Thanks to this app you can easily manage your mobile WiFi directly from smartphone or tablet.

LINK APP displays in real time the status of the connection and data speeds, battery life and SMS. Through the app you can set monthly data usage plan and you\'ll be automatically disconnected once you reach preset limit.
Through LINK APP you can block any device trying to connect to your WiFi hotspot with no permission. And you\'ll also be free to edit user\'s name to easily recognize them.
